is\nof high multistream field resolution and low softening length, the halo\nsubstructures with local multistream maxima are isolated as individual halo\nsites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Jun 2017 19:18:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-26"}
